1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I have consulted with the minister</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>about the date of your wedding.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

2
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:05,440
<font color="#ffffff"><i>We have agreed on</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>the beginning of next month.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

3
00:00:05,520 --> 00:00:08,200
<font color="#ffffff">Do not worry about</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">what hasn't yet happened.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

4
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:10,240
<font color="#ffffff"><i>The best we can do is</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>make the most of today.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

5
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:11,760
<font color="#ffffff">I know my father better than anyone.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

6
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:13,320
<font color="#ffffff">Run?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

7
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,520
<font color="#ffffff">You die today.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

8
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:17,240
<font color="#ffffff">PREVIOUS EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

9
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,840
<font color="#ffffff">Let me dry your hair.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

10
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,200
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I can do it myself.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

11
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:21,440
<font color="#ffffff">Grandmother.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

12
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:23,840
<font color="#ffffff">Come with me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

13
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:27,520
<font color="#ffffff">You two can stay at his place</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for as long as you like.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

14
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:53,200
<font color="#ffffff">A flute is quite difficult</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to play, isn't it?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

15
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:55,920
<font color="#ffffff">You just need to be sure to cover</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the holes to stop the air from leaking.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

16
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,040
<font color="#ffffff">My fingers are small.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

17
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:00,880
<font color="#ffffff">Show me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

18
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,440
<font color="#ffffff">You are certainly right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

19
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:12,440
<font color="#ffffff">My fingers are small, unlike yours.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Your fingers are gigantic.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

20
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:17,240
<font color="#ffffff">Let me help then.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

21
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,760
<font color="#ffffff">Cover the holes with your fingers.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

22
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,360
<font color="#ffffff">Make sure they're completely covered.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

23
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,880
<font color="#ffffff">Now try it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

24
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:54,040
<font color="#ffffff">No leaky sound!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

25
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,400
<font color="#ffffff">See?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

26
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:58,040
<font color="#ffffff">We make everything better</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">when we do it together.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

27
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,840
<font color="#ffffff">Keep playing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

28
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,039
<font color="#ffffff">Thee!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

29
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,080
<font color="#ffffff">Ram!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

30
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:42,360
<font color="#ffffff">How could you not know</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">where your own son is?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

31
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:45,240
<font color="#ffffff">He's your grandson too, Mother.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

32
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,520
<font color="#ffffff">Are you talking back?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

33
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:50,000
<font color="#ffffff">I contacted the ministry where he works,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

34
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,560
<font color="#ffffff">and found that</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">he has asked for leave of absence.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

35
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,120
<font color="#ffffff">He's ruining his career.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

36
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:57,720
<font color="#ffffff">What shall we do with his wedding?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

37
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,280
<font color="#ffffff">It is only seven days away.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

38
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,040
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sure he will be back by then.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

39
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:06,360
<font color="#ffffff">Professor Rati is to embark for France</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in seven days too.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

40
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,920
<font color="#ffffff">Thee will definitely be back.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

41
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,120
<font color="#ffffff">Please rest easy, Mother.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

42
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:12,320
<font color="#ffffff">You want me to "rest easy"</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">when my grandson has run off with a ma--<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

43
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,720
<font color="#ffffff">With someone?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

44
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,720
<font color="#ffffff">I will not wait a whole week.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

45
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:24,040
<font color="#ffffff">You must have someone fetch him back</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">as soon as possible.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

46
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,960
<font color="#ffffff">This is an order!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

47
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:50,480
<font color="#ffffff">The document you asked</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Tiwa to translate, sir.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

48
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,280
<font color="#ffffff">I told you not to say his name.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

49
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,040
<font color="#ffffff">I know very well who it is from.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

50
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:04,920
<font color="#ffffff">He's very good.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

51
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,040
<font color="#ffffff">I'll be at the dining table.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

52
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,880
<font color="#ffffff">Bring the car around</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to pick me up out back.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

53
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:13,920
<font color="#ffffff">Do not let anyone tell my mother</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">that I'll dine at Ruedi's.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

54
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,920
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

55
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,560
<font color="#ffffff">Thanks.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

56
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,000
<font color="#ffffff">Mek!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

57
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,520
<font color="#ffffff">You must be tired.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

58
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,320
<font color="#ffffff">Water?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

59
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,400
<font color="#ffffff">I am indeed thirsty.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

60
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,800
<font color="#ffffff">Think you're funny?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

61
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,400
<font color="#ffffff">I'm only teasing you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

62
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,800
<font color="#ffffff">I'm worried about you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">since you've walked all this way.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

63
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,560
<font color="#ffffff">-You are?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Yes.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

64
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,960
<font color="#ffffff">I'm the host, after all.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I must take good care of my guests.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

65
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,480
<font color="#ffffff">So this is your mother's place?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

66
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,520
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

67
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,800
<font color="#ffffff">I grew up on this land.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

68
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,400
<font color="#ffffff">To think, I nearly lost it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

69
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,120
<font color="#ffffff">Are you moving back here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

70
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:21,520
<font color="#ffffff">-Alone?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-I doubt anyone wants to live here.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

71
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,480
<font color="#ffffff">It's inconvenient.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

72
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:26,360
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sure even the servants' quarters</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">at Suriyakorn Palace are better.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

73
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,960
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not one to be put off by hardship.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

74
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,600
<font color="#ffffff">It's very hard out here, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

75
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,320
<font color="#ffffff">I can endure it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

76
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,800
<font color="#ffffff">By all means, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

77
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:38,160
<font color="#ffffff">You are always welcome here, Young Master.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

78
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,520
<font color="#ffffff">Let's go.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

79
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,760
<font color="#ffffff">Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

80
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,800
<font color="#ffffff">Aren't you coming?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

81
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,920
<font color="#ffffff">You're not going to help me carry these?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

82
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,440
<font color="#ffffff">My hands are full.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

83
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,000
<font color="#ffffff">Come on, Dech.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

84
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,760
<font color="#ffffff">This is one of the hardships</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I must endure, I guess.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

85
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,560
<font color="#ffffff">-My lord!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Ow!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

86
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,880
<font color="#ffffff">-Thee, stop it!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Rati, don't hit me!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

87
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,160
<font color="#ffffff">-Ow!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-I told you not to do that!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

88
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,800
<font color="#ffffff">Hello, Professor.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

89
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,960
<font color="#ffffff">Hello.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

90
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,360
<font color="#ffffff">What were you two playing, sirs?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

91
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:37,880
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you, Mek, for letting us stay here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

92
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,560
<font color="#ffffff">Professor Rati was kind enough</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to give me lessons.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

93
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,320
<font color="#ffffff">How could I not help?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

94
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,400
<font color="#ffffff">We intend to stay here</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">until the translator exam.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

95
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,360
<font color="#ffffff">We won't be going back</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to Suriyakorn Palace<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

96
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,800
<font color="#ffffff">for fear of being harassed by Father.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

97
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:56,200
<font color="#ffffff">The exam is in six days.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

98
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,080
<font color="#ffffff">We want to be as focused as we can.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

99
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,200
<font color="#ffffff">While staying here,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

100
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:04,600
<font color="#ffffff">we must bother you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">with some lessons, Professor.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

101
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,880
<font color="#ffffff">Of course.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

102
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:06,960
<font color="#ffffff">It'd be my pleasure.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

103
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,800
<font color="#ffffff">Shall we eat before the food gets cold?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

104
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,400
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you again, Dech, Mek.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

105
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:18,720
<font color="#ffffff">Rati and I will only stay seven days,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">since Rati must embark for France then.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

106
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:22,680
<font color="#ffffff">You are leaving in seven days?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

107
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,720
<font color="#ffffff">Count,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

108
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:30,000
<font color="#ffffff">Her Highness refuses to call off</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the wedding between you and Lady Pa.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

109
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,880
<font color="#ffffff">They are preparing for the occasion.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

110
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:38,320
<font color="#ffffff">I heard the wedding will be held</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the day after the professor leaves.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

111
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:42,919
<font color="#ffffff">Are you… going to attend it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

112
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:20,400
<font color="#ffffff">Do what you should.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

113
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,800
<font color="#ffffff">The wedding will happen anyway.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

114
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,720
<font color="#ffffff">It is inevitable.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

115
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,880
<font color="#ffffff">We should not cause people</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">any more trouble.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

116
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,640
<font color="#ffffff">Have we caused anybody trouble?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

117
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:36,240
<font color="#ffffff">I have done what was expected</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">of me all my life.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

118
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:40,120
<font color="#ffffff">Is it really impossible for me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to do what I want for once?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

119
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,640
<font color="#ffffff">We have no choice but to part.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

120
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,320
<font color="#ffffff">Don't say that.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

121
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,800
<font color="#ffffff">At least not right now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

122
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,000
<font color="#ffffff">Thee.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

123
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,440
<font color="#ffffff">I won't mention it again.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

124
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,720
<font color="#ffffff">These seven days before you leave…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

125
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,200
<font color="#ffffff">please think of nothing but us.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

126
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,600
<font color="#ffffff">Let me hold you just a little longer.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

127
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,480
<font color="#ffffff">Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

128
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,480
<font color="#ffffff">Dech.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

129
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,520
<font color="#ffffff">Dech!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

130
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,800
<font color="#ffffff">Ow!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

131
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:08,640
<font color="#ffffff">-What was that for?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Be quiet.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

132
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,840
<font color="#ffffff">You're distracting me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

133
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,680
<font color="#ffffff">Focus.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

134
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,960
<font color="#ffffff">You've been at it this whole morning.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

135
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,080
<font color="#ffffff">Aren't you tired?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

136
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,440
<font color="#ffffff">I'm willing to be tired today</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for an easier tomorrow.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

137
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:27,400
<font color="#ffffff">It seems you really want to</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">become a translator.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

138
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,800
<font color="#ffffff">I do want to, yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

139
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,520
<font color="#ffffff">But I also want to be your friend.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

140
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:37,840
<font color="#ffffff">Now people won't be able to say that</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">your friend is a lowly servant.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

141
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,000
<font color="#ffffff">Are you talking about my father?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

142
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,600
<font color="#ffffff">As for you,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

143
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:43,680
<font color="#ffffff">don't you want the job too?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

144
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:46,400
<font color="#ffffff">You should take it more seriously.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

145
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:51,480
<font color="#ffffff">My friend works harder than an ant.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I won't give up so easily either.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

146
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,520
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Tu peux y arriver.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

147
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,200
<font color="#ffffff">"You can do it."</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

148
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,200
<font color="#ffffff">You're good.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

149
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:58,880
<font color="#ffffff">Don't you underestimate me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

150
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:06,280
<font color="#ffffff">Not to brag, but I remember every word</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in <font color="#ffffff"><font color="#ffffff"><i>Dictionarius Linguae Thai.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font></font>

151
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:09,720
<font color="#ffffff">It's </font><font color="#ffffff"><font color="#ffffff"><i>Dictionarium Linguae Thai.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

152
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:13,440
<font color="#ffffff">Stop hitting me already!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not your dependent, you know.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

153
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,000
<font color="#ffffff">I wouldn't mind providing for you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

154
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,760
<font color="#ffffff">What are you even saying?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

155
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,640
<font color="#ffffff">Pay attention.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

156
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,320
<font color="#ffffff">Which part are you working on?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

157
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:25,320
<font color="#ffffff">This one.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

158
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,040
<font color="#ffffff">Look at you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

159
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,760
<font color="#ffffff">Your hair is all messy after that nap.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

160
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:47,080
<font color="#ffffff">Look at you. Your hair is all frizzy</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">after thinking so hard.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

161
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,520
<font color="#ffffff">Look at you, playing with words.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

162
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,800
<font color="#ffffff">Are you pranking me?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

